HEADWORD: Exothermic
<hw>Ex`o*ther"mic</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[Pref.
<ets>exo-</ets> + <ets>thermic</ets>.]</ety> <fld>(Chem.)</fld>
